# Swat 4, with Flydigi Apex 2 in mind
PovXY WASD  # Move with D-pad
JoyX Q E # Lean left or right
CamXY flick # Turn with right stick

PaddleLeft C  # Hold to Crouch
ActionL Shift  # Toggle Sprint

TriggerR M1  # Shoot
TriggerL M2 # Hold for commands
BumperR X # Toggle firing mode

ActionR F  # Use
ActionA R  # Reload
BumperL Z  # Zoom

MenuL M # + Calibrate # Show objectives / output calibration data
MenuR Escape # Pause

ActionD Ctrl # Prepare Command
PaddleRight Tab # Cycle command group

ActionH Layer 1 # Grenade selection
ActionV Layer 2 # Door tools
ActionB Layer 3 # Pacifying tools
ActionC Layer 4 # Commands
PinkyLeft Layer 5 # Weapons

Layer 1 # Grenade selection
CamXY 3 5 4 4 # Stinger Stinger Flash CS

Layer 2 # Door tools
CamXY 8 0 7 9 # Toolkit Wedge Breach Optiwand

Layer 3 # Pacifying subjects
CamXY 6 H 6 H # Pepper / Handcuffs

Layer 4 # Commands
BumperL Insert # Cycle Red Team Viewport
BumperR Home # Cycle Blue Team Viewport
ActionL PageUp # Cycle Sniper Team Viewport
MenuL Backspace # Control Active Viewport
ActionR Space # Quick Command

Layer 5 # Weapons
ActionH 1 # Primary
ActionB 2 # Secondary
ActionV V # Flashlight
ActionA L # Light Stick
